getAuthenticationToken.docs: Retrieve an authentication token for the API

getUserInformation.docs: Retrieve detailed information about a specific user

__package__.yml.rawContents:
errors:
  UnauthorizedError:
    status-code: 401
    type: unknown
    docs: Unauthorized
  NotFoundError:
    status-code: 404
    type: unknown
    docs: User not found
service:
  auth: false
  base-path: ''
  endpoints:
    listUsers:
      path: /users
      method: GET
      auth: false
      docs: List information about all users
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      display-name: List Users
      response:
        docs: Successful response
        type: User
      errors:
        - UnauthorizedError
        - NotFoundError
      examples:
        - response:
            body: {}
    getUserInformation:
      path: /users/{userId}
      method: GET
      auth: false
      docs: Retrieve detailed information about a specific user
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      path-parameters:
        userId: string
      display-name: Get user information
      response:
        docs: Successful response
        type: User
      errors:
        - UnauthorizedError
        - NotFoundError
      examples:
        - path-parameters:
            userId: userId
          response:
            body: {}
    getAuthenticationToken:
      path: /token
      method: GET
      auth: false
      docs: Retrieve an authentication token for the API
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      display-name: Get authentication token
      response:
        docs: Successful response
        type: Token
      errors:
        - UnauthorizedError
      examples:
        - response:
            body: {}
  source:
    openapi: ../openapi.yml
types:
  User:
    properties:
      id: optional<string>
      username: optional<string>
      email: optional<string>
      createdAt: optional<datetime>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  Token:
    properties:
      accessToken: optional<string>
      tokenType: optional<string>
      expiresIn: optional<integer>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml

rootApiFile.rawContents:
name: api
error-discrimination:
  strategy: status-code
display-name: User and Token API
environments:
  Default: https://a.com
default-environment: Default
